{"tid":454123,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"女子深水埗遇襲　粉臉受傷痛到咀歪","createTime":"2017-10-31T23:55:29.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-01T00:12:34.000Z","uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"d06e4108952d0bc0221b66c63915495b620c90eb","tid":454123,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T23:55:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20171101/photo/bkn-20171101042919475-1101_00822_001_01b.jpg?20171101072839\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20171101%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20171101042919475-1101_00822_001_01b.jpg%3F20171101072839&h=a71c497f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n遇襲女子送院。(胡德威攝)<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20171101/photo/bkn-20171101042919475-1101_00822_001_02b.jpg?20171101072839\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20171101%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20171101042919475-1101_00822_001_02b.jpg%3F20171101072839&h=ff02e057&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n警員在場調查。(胡德威攝)<br />\n<br />\n深水埗發生傷人案，凌晨3時許，一名年約30歲女子，途經北河街與荔枝角道交界，疑因故與人爭執，突遭對方襲擊，額頭、臉及右手受傷，兇徒傷人後逃去，女事主報警求助。<br />\n<br />\n警員到場調查，並在附近兜截，惟無發現。女事主由救護車送往醫院時狀甚痛苦，臉容扭曲，情緒激動。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20171101/bkn-20171101042919475-1101_00822_001.html?refer=hn2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20171101%2Fbkn-20171101042919475-1101_00822_001.html%3Frefer%3Dhn2&d=r%2B%2FiB006GaAC7ImnPZ1QyaWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=f7171cfe\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20171101/bkn-20171101042919475-1101_00822_001.html?refer=hn2</a>"},{"pid":"9e08586c555e6bdb2779fafc2a8f5440cc291e40","tid":454123,"uid":38946,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T23:56:45.000Z","msg":"高潮緊?"},{"pid":"53b6917d110a9b64c67afcee1a6515af75ab5293","tid":454123,"uid":54747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T00:06